{
  "Crossbow Expert": {
    "description": "Thanks to extensive practice with the crossbow, you gain the following benefits:\nYou ignore the loading quality of crossbows with which you are proficient.\nBeing within 5 feet of a hostile creature doesn't impose disadvantage on your ranged attack rolls.\nWhen you use the Attack action and attack with a one-handed weapon, you can use a bonus action to attack with a loaded hand crossbow you are holding."
  }
